OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,FA critical incident at University
OL,7,FHospital Southampton is likely to stay
OL,8,Fin place for "some days" even if
OL,9,Ftemperatures cool, its chief medical
OL,10,Fofficer has warned.
OL,12,FPaul Grundy told ITV Meridian that he
OL,13,Fexpects patient numbers to remain high
OL,14,F"beyond the end of the heatwave".
OL,16,FHe added that the hospital's executive
OL,17,Fteam is meeting "a number of times a
OL,18,Fday" to discuss the critical incident
OL,19,Fstatus and will step it down "as soon
OL,20,Fas it's possible".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
