FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,FA critical incident was announced on
OL,7,FThursday because of the extreme heat,
OL,8,Fwhich has broken temperature records
OL,9,Ffor June.
OL,11,FHospitals declare such incidents when
OL,12,Fthey are experiencing exceptional
OL,13,Flevels of pressure to its services and
OL,14,Fcan no longer function normally.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,FMr Grundy said: "I would just give a
OL,7,Fwarning that even if the temperature
OL,8,Fcools over the next couple of days,
OL,9,Fthe predictions from public health are
OL,10,Fthat the illness in society due to the
OL,11,Fheat will continue beyond the end of
OL,12,Fthe heatwave.
OL,14,F"We are still expecting over the next
OL,15,Ffew days additional workload coming in
OL,16,Ffrom patients coming into the hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,F"I think the critical incident for the
OL,7,Fmoment is going to have to stay in
OL,8,Fplace for a few days. Obviously, we
OL,9,Fmeet a number of times a day to
OL,10,Fdiscuss that and as soon as it's
OL,11,Fpossible to step that down we will."
OL,13,FThe hospital has cancelled a number of
OL,14,Fplanned operations as well as some
OL,15,Foutpatient appointments.
OL,17,FPeople are being asked to only attend
OL,18,Fits accident and emergency department
OL,19,Fif they have an immediate life
OL,20,Fthreatening injury or condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,FAdvice has also been issued for people
OL,7,Fto use alternative healthcare options
OL,8,Ffor non-urgent medical issues,
OL,9,Fwhenever possible, such as community
OL,10,Fpharmacies, GP practices, urgent
OL,11,Ftreatment centres and NHS 111.
OL,13,FSimilar incidents have been declared
OL,14,Fat Portsmouth's Queen Alexandra
OL,15,FHospital and the South East Coast
OL,16,FAmbulance Service (Secamb).
OL,18,FThe former made the decision on
OL,19,FWednesday after the extreme heat
OL,20,Fcaused some of its chiller units to
OL,21,Ffail.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhilst they are now up and running,
OL,12,Fthe exceptionally hot weather has
OL,13,Fmeant that cooling back down vital
OL,14,Finfrastructure on site is taking much
OL,15,Flonger than normal.
OL,17,FThe hospital said that some planned
OL,18,Fcare and appointments will continue to
OL,19,Fbe stood down until temperatures have
OL,20,Fstabilised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782497914
OL,3,CHospital to remain under critical
OL,4,Cincident status for 'some days'
OL,6,FAnyone impacted by the disruption will
OL,7,Fbe contacted directly.
OL,9,FSecamb, meanwhile, said it declared a
OL,10,Fcritical incident on Thursday after
OL,11,Fexperiencing "one of the busiest days
OL,12,Fwe have seen this year".
OL,14,F"While the heat is expected to
OL,15,Fdissipate in the next few days, we
OL,16,Fexpect demand to remain high and will
OL,17,Fcontinue to put in place all possible
OL,18,Fmeasures to ensure we return to a
OL,19,Fnormal service as quickly as
OL,20,Fpossible," said Secamb Strategic
OL,21,FCommander, James Pavey.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
